	"data": "<div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>۞يَٰبَنِيٓ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> ءَادَمَ <a data-content='البسوا ثيابكم لستر عوراتكم' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>خُذُواْ زِينَتَكُمۡ</a> عِندَ كُلِّ مَسۡجِدٖ وَكُلُواْ </div><div>وَٱشۡرَبُواْ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>وَلَا</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> تُسۡرِفُوٓاْۚ إِنَّهُۥ لَا يُحِبُّ ٱلۡمُسۡرِفِينَ ٣١ قُلۡ مَنۡ حَرَّمَ زِينَةَ </div><div>ٱللَّهِ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>ٱلَّتِيٓ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> أَخۡرَجَ لِعِبَادِهِۦ وَٱلطَّيِّبَٰتِ مِنَ ٱلرِّزۡقِۚ قُلۡ هِيَ لِلَّذِينَ </div><div>ءَامَنُواْ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>فِي</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> ٱلۡحَيَوٰةِ ٱلدُّنۡيَا خَالِصَةٗ يَوۡمَ ٱلۡقِيَٰمَةِۗ كَذَٰلِكَ نُفَصِّلُ </div><div>ٱلۡأٓيَٰتِ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>لِقَوۡمٖ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> يَعۡلَمُونَ ٣٢ قُلۡ إِنَّمَا حَرَّمَ رَبِّيَ <a data-content='كبائر المعاصي لمزيد قبحها' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>ٱلۡفَوَٰحِشَ</a> مَا ظَهَرَ مِنۡهَا </div><div>وَمَا</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>بَطَنَ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> <a data-content='ما يوجبه من سائر المعاصي' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>وَٱلۡإِثۡمَ</a> <a data-content='الظلم والإستطالة على الناس' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>وَٱلۡبَغۡيَ</a> بِغَيۡرِ ٱلۡحَقِّ وَأَن تُشۡرِكُواْ بِٱللَّهِ مَا لَمۡ </div><div>يُنَزِّلۡ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>بِهِۦ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> <a data-content='حجةً وبرهاناً' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>سُلۡطَٰنٗا</a> وَأَن تَقُولُواْ عَلَى ٱللَّهِ مَا لَا تَعۡلَمُونَ ٣٣ وَلِكُلِّ </div><div>أُمَّةٍ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>أَجَلٞۖ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> فَإِذَا جَآءَ أَجَلُهُمۡ لَا يَسۡتَأۡخِرُونَ سَاعَةٗ وَلَا </div><div>يَسۡتَقۡدِمُونَ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.4vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>٣٤</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> يَٰبَنِيٓ ءَادَمَ إِمَّا يَأۡتِيَنَّكُمۡ رُسُلٞ مِّنكُمۡ يَقُصُّونَ عَلَيۡكُمۡ ءَايَٰتِي </div><div>فَمَنِ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>ٱتَّقَىٰ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> وَأَصۡلَحَ فَلَا خَوۡفٌ عَلَيۡهِمۡ وَلَا هُمۡ يَحۡزَنُونَ ٣٥ وَٱلَّذِينَ </div><div>كَذَّبُواْ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>بِ‍َٔايَٰتِنَا</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> وَٱسۡتَكۡبَرُواْ عَنۡهَآ أُوْلَٰٓئِكَ أَصۡحَٰبُ ٱلنَّارِۖ هُمۡ </div><div>فِيهَا</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>خَٰلِدُونَ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> ٣٦ فَمَنۡ أَظۡلَمُ مِمَّنِ ٱفۡتَرَىٰ عَلَى ٱللَّهِ كَذِبًا أَوۡ </div><div>كَذَّبَ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>بِ‍َٔايَٰتِهِۦٓۚ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> أُوْلَٰٓئِكَ يَنَالُهُمۡ نَصِيبُهُم مِّنَ ٱلۡكِتَٰب